WEBVTT

00:01:01.007 --> 00:01:03.743
This program is called:
New ways of thinking,

00:01:03.767 --> 00:01:09.023
and you must be wondering,
"Why am I discussing old ideas?"

00:01:09.047 --> 00:01:11.183
My name is Manu Prakash,

00:01:11.207 --> 00:01:13.903
and I spend most of my time figuring out

00:01:13.927 --> 00:01:19.823
how we can get children all over the world
to “feel” science.

00:01:19.847 --> 00:01:24.143
Not just read science but do science.

00:01:24.167 --> 00:01:31.167
In this world, over a billion people live
without electricity, roads and clinics.